description: The Pirate, coming off her win with Xana, looks at tiny Jenya (4'11") like a pit bull looks at a cat. Jenya has grit, determination and spunk going for her, but that is not enough by far. This was the first and last attempt at nipple submissions, there was a reason we had no pinching in our rules, and I just needed to be reminded. Pinching causes anger, the wrong kind of anger. The Pirate is undefeated lifetime, who is going to stop her?
title: The Pirate (1-0) vs. Jenya (0-0)
